    "data": [
        {
            "title": "西隧4車「串燒」式相撞 私家車疑收掣不及肇禍 男子痛苦哀嚎",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/657617748675e483571f5d93741f0cc1/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041107205971550.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>西隧昨日發生4車「串燒」式相撞事件。根據網上流傳短片，昨日(10日)上午11時許，一輛掛上中港牌的白色私家車甫駛入西區海底隧道，疑因交通情況收慢車速，尾隨私家車收掣不及，「追尾」撞個正着，短片內傳出「嘭」一聲巨響，疑似涉事的男司機亦相繼發出痛苦哀嚎聲。\n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p> \n\n</p>\n<p>警方表示，昨日早上約11時19分，西隧往香港方向有數輛私家車，因應路面情況減慢，惟尾隨的35歲姓楊私家車男司機收掣不及，撞向前車32歲姓黃男司機的私家車，造成4車相撞，事件中無人受傷。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063323/即時-港聞-西隧4車-串燒-式相撞-私家車疑收掣不及肇禍-男子痛苦哀嚎",
            "pub_date": "2025-04-11 07:26:25",
            "source": "stheadline",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "歐霸│里昂2:2曼聯 奧拿拿唔爭氣 2度送禮累紅魔補時被追和",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"奧拿拿唔爭氣，2度送禮累紅魔補時被追和。路透社\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/b9636fe6d690cdaf73ab011052ae7c0a/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041107104478279.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">奧拿拿唔爭氣，2度送禮累紅魔補時被追和。路透社</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>周四歐霸8強首回合，曼聯作客里昂在先失一球下，一度反超前2:1，可是在補時5分鐘失守被追和2:2，斷送好局。紅魔和波罪人，就是門將奧拿拿，這位在賽前與里昂的前曼聯中場尼曼查馬迪大打口水戰的喀麥隆國門，分別因為判斷錯誤和甩手而兩度失守，自己在「仇人」面前唔爭氣，難怪被譏諷為紅魔史上最差門將。\n\n</p><h2>奧拿拿2次犯錯累失波</h2>\n<p>里昂於25分鐘先開紀錄，左翼堤亞高艾美達左路開出罰球，皮球越過中間的人堆，再在門前彈地而起，奧拿拿判斷錯誤讓它溜入遠柱。曼聯之後站穩腳，先在換邊前一次罰球攻勢中，中場文路爾烏加迪於禁區頂半傳半射，中堅利萊約路頂入扳平，到88分鐘一次快速反擊，隊長般奴費南迪斯傳中，射手約舒亞舒克斯接應頂槌要入，反超前2:1。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿判斷錯誤，被里昂直接彎入罰球。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6bd537c0c97f60be3859fd1504a2add2/2025-04/1_18.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿判斷錯誤，被里昂直接彎入罰球。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿要為第一個失球負責。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/16112ca967feb18696b560492f12b28d/2025-04/3_17.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿要為第一個失球負責。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿判斷錯誤。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5aafe8f16b456a0e90839e2f129dc5bd/2025-04/4_19.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿判斷錯誤。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"堤亞高艾美達為里昂先開紀錄。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bca544dab148eadb77306b2dbc3183f0/2025-04/5_16.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        堤亞高艾美達為里昂先開紀錄。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利萊約路頂入，為曼聯追和1:1。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4decde0701bc37b33b555fdb3568b4fa/2025-04/6_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利萊約路頂入，為曼聯追和1:1。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利萊約路為曼聯追和1:1。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/515f97cbbf8c27de72910b6607622d9e/2025-04/7_11.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利萊約路為曼聯追和1:1。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"約舒亞舒克斯於88分鐘頂成2:1。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7a5d4760808f4349fab56f774789e15e/2025-04/8_10.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約舒亞舒克斯於88分鐘頂成2:1。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"約舒亞舒克斯於88分鐘頂成2:1。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9726c1a650e36c85ef9f38af4436f0c9/2025-04/9_6.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約舒亞舒克斯於88分鐘頂成2:1。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"約舒亞舒克斯入波後，展示招牌的慶祝動作。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5a09130796d7472ac7d1b7b5a15cb74b/2025-04/10_5.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        約舒亞舒克斯入波後，展示招牌的慶祝動作。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>完場前接波甩手</h2>\n<p>以為曼聯先拔頭籌之際，里昂前鋒米卡捷達於補時5分鐘在12碼點抽射，角度太正中原本沒有威脅，可是奧拿拿接波甩手，主隊前鋒卓基衝前補射破網追和2:2完場，雙方下周次回合在奧脫福球場再分勝負。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿接波甩手，被卓基補射破網扳平。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/77d932154b8b15dba3e05f38cdd67b54/2025-04/11_4.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿接波甩手，被卓基補射破網扳平。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿接波甩手，被卓基補射破網扳平。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/39c48f99358490825ee16f728d7781ce/2025-04/12_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿接波甩手，被卓基補射破網扳平。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"卓基把握奧拿拿犯錯，為里昂追和2:2。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/59e13e1e6ffc4514598a9189d7f75da5/2025-04/13_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        卓基把握奧拿拿犯錯，為里昂追和2:2。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"卓基把握奧拿拿犯錯，為里昂追和2:2。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2636393fb4c197277c6a037f52cd4293/2025-04/14_2.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        卓基把握奧拿拿犯錯，為里昂追和2:2。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿今場2次犯錯。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e96c631fa18b0ad4c9a149e5720c1bea/2025-04/15_3.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿今場2次犯錯。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"奧拿拿今場2次犯錯。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/47ba4f63f8cb26393a1ccd86f5ccf94e/2025-04/16_1.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        奧拿拿今場2次犯錯。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"曼聯中場卡斯米路對和波十分失望。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/58428414f9186f72ef899d6718868b03/2025-04/17_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        曼聯中場卡斯米路對和波十分失望。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"利萊約路面露不悅。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8c75219630b313251f352660083857a6/2025-04/18_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        利萊約路面露不悅。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"般奴費南迪斯面無表情。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6500490ff170ee3ddf1b465cc4f9d893/2025-04/19.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        般奴費南迪斯面無表情。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"魯賓艾摩廉未能領軍羸波。路透社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d7d4275269ad919b49476f2f664d0e2c/2025-04/20_0.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        魯賓艾摩廉未能領軍羸波。路透社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>近5任曼聯主力門將 奧拿拿數據最差</h2>\n<p>奧拿拿今場賽前與曾效力曼聯的里昂中場尼曼查馬迪爆發口水戰，一度被後者譏諷為紅魔史上最差門將，但今場自己唔爭氣2次犯錯累球隊和波，今仗坐足90分鐘板凳沒有上陣的馬迪，就在後備席上見到「仇人」出醜。連同今仗，奧拿拿加盟紅魔後已失掉139球，場均失1.48球，是曼聯近5任主力門將中平均失球最多的一位；上一任之力迪基亞場均失1.08球，再之前3位巴夫斯、舒米高和雲達沙，分別是0.98、0.82和0.76球。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
