        {
            "title": "將軍澳CAPRI 簡潔長廳時尚雅緻 外望開揚市景",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"將軍澳CAPRI 簡潔長廳時尚雅緻 外望開揚市景\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/af167958778e3d4c006b5a9bcf1d0a53/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250410/_2025041017372895890.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">將軍澳CAPRI 簡潔長廳時尚雅緻 外望開揚市景</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>將軍澳屋苑CAPRI，周邊配套完善，加上毗鄰將軍澳海濱公園，打造愜意都會生活。是次為大家介紹當中的8座中層D室，實用面積535方呎，為2房間隔，開揚企理，間隔實用，現以850萬放盤，實用呎價約15888元。\n\n</p>\n<p>進入單位，即見廳堂四正寬敞，間隔實用，易於擺放傢俬，裝潢方面，以淺木地板配以白色牆身，保養新淨，現時飯廳放置可延伸飯桌，附落地玻璃連露台，可望區內樓景，周圍有樹木環繞。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4188159/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"單位可望區內樓景，周圍有樹木環繞，綠意盎然。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f7157a92e49cb595e81912328fe61905/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_30_AM_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        單位可望區內樓景，周圍有樹木環繞，綠意盎然。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4188160/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"主人房設地台，存放四季衣物，設計實用。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cb1bb4275942e41b387d3aed4c07902b/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_30_AM_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        主人房設地台，存放四季衣物，設計實用。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4188161/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"明廁內有齊全潔具，配有鏡櫃及浴櫃。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/03e56934c12e987c45503531ed372fda/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_30_AM_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        明廁內有齊全潔具，配有鏡櫃及浴櫃。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4188162/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"將軍澳屋苑CAPRI 8座中層D室，實用面積535方呎，現叫價850萬。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/46c0b1bda983be0430d4e81b02f1c0ec/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-09_at_10_04_30_AM.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        將軍澳屋苑CAPRI 8座中層D室，實用面積535方呎，現叫價850萬。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4188163/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"CAPRI外貌。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/824339f58875cd6f1c900684d369e33c/2025-04/749_ATF_03.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        CAPRI外貌。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p><h2>535呎2房開則</h2>\n<p>單位間隔為2房，睡房設計方正，均設大窗。主人房設地台，存放四季衣物，並靠窗擺放雙人牀，並於一旁放置書桌，可以於此工作。明廁有備透氣窗，光潔明亮，內設有大鏡及浴缸。廚房方面，備L形上下廚櫃，容量充足。\n\n</p>\n<p>會德豐旗下屋苑CAPRI，由10座大樓及13幢洋房組成，提供超過420個單位，涵蓋1房至4房間隔。\n\n</p><h2>必睇靚位</h2>\n<p>位於將軍澳站及調景嶺站之間\n\n</p>\n<p>廳房開揚企理\n\n</p>\n<p>2房間隔方正實用\n\n</p>\n<p>自設基座商場\n\n</p><h2>放盤單位資料 </h2>\n<p>物業名稱：CAPRI\n\n</p>\n<p>地址：唐賢街33號\n\n</p>\n<p>樓齡：7年\n\n</p>\n<p>單位：8座中層D室\n\n</p>\n<p>實用面積：535方呎\n\n</p>\n<p>間隔：2房\n\n</p>\n<p>叫價：850萬元\n\n</p>\n<p>呎價：15888元\n\n</p>\n<p>代理行：美聯物業\n\n</p>\n<p>電話：6103 2324（蔡小姐）\n\n</p>\n<p>*相片由代理行提供\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2063246/即時-地產-將軍澳CAPRI-簡潔長廳時尚雅緻-外望開揚市景",
